Usage: report_instance_cdb [-help] [<objectListOrCollection>]
                           [-analysis_type {early late}] [-output_file <string>]
                           [-quiet] [-view <string>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<objectListOrCollection>     # Leaf-instances, or hierarchical modules
                             # SDC-style wildcarding supported (string, optional)
-analysis_type {early late}  # Specifies the analysis type for the query
                             # (enum, optional)
-output_file <string>        # Specifies the output filename, Default: Display
                             # on screen. (string, optional)
-quiet                       # suppress warning messages for cells missing in
                             # CDB files (bool, optional)
-view <string>               # Specifies the view names. Default: all views.
                             # (string, optional)